
Program to identify objects.

Software Used:

The Robot Operating System: 

	The base platform. In future will be used to implement callbacks.

Open Computer Vision(OpenCV): 

	Uses the webcam for see the world. Reads and writes images. Implementaion of Oriented FAST and Rotated BRIEF (ORB) for image comparision.

CloudSight: 

	The Web API used to recognize objects.

Segmentaion: 

	Implementation of the segmentation algorithm described in: Efficient Graph-Based Image Segmentation Pedro F. Felzenszwalb and 	        Daniel P. Huttenlocher International Journal of Computer Vision, 59(2) September 2004.




